 Services</h2><p><strong>Everything you need to turn traffic into bookings and sales.</strong></p><p>We build practical systems for Newcastle businesses, then keep improving them each month.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row row-small\"><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6ebf2;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;height:100%;\"><h3>POS Setup &amp; Integration</h3><ul><li>Square or Lightspeed setup</li><li>Inventory and menu sync</li><li>Staff workflow and training</li><li>Launch checklist and handover</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6ebf2;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;height:100%;\"><h3>Website &amp; Online Ordering</h3><ul><li>Conversion-focused website build</li><li>Online payment and checkout flow</li><li>QR ordering and booking systems</li><li>Mobile-first speed optimisation</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6ebf2;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;height:100%;\"><h3>Growth Channels</h3><ul><li>Google Business Profile setup</li><li>Review and reputation management</li><li>Local SEO improvements</li><li>Social media setup and baseline plan</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"row row-small\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\"><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7e5ff;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;height:100%;\"><h3>Starter Package</h3><p><em>For new small businesses.</em></p><ul><li>POS setup</li><li>Basic website</li><li>Google profile setup</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #2f6df6;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;height:100%;\"><h3>Growth Package</h3><p><em>For businesses ready to scale.</em></p><ul><li>Online ordering flow</li><li>SEO optimisation</li>