:1px solid #e6ebf2;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;height:100%;\"><h3>Growth Channels</h3><ul><li>Google Business Profile setup</li><li>Review and reputation management</li><li>Local SEO improvements</li><li>Social media setup and baseline plan</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"row row-small\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\"><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7e5ff;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;height:100%;\"><h3>Starter Package</h3><p><em>For new small businesses.</em></p><ul><li>POS setup</li><li>Basic website</li><li>Google profile setup</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #2f6df6;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;height:100%;\"><h3>Growth Package</h3><p><em>For businesses ready to scale.</em></p><ul><li>Online ordering flow</li><li>SEO optimisation</li><li>Social setup</li><li>Review strategy</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"col small-12 medium-4\"><div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7e5ff;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;height:100%;\"><h3>Pro Package</h3><p><em>For established businesses.</em></p><ul><li>Full system integration</li><li>Ads management</li><li>CRM workflow support</li><li>Monthly optimisation</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-top:18px;\"><div class=\"col small-12 large-12\"><div class=\"col-inner\"><p><a class=\"button primary is-large\" href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/free-newcastle-business-audit/\">Start With a Free Business Audit</a></p><p>Need help now? Call <a href=\"tel:0240755307\">02 40755307</a> or email <a href=\"mailto:hello@newcastlehub.info\">hello@newcastlehub.info</a>.</p></div></div></div></div></section>\n\n",
